sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Project
    participant Asset
    participant Commerce
    participant Workflow
    participant Production
    participant Base44

    User->>Project: Create or open project
    User->>Asset: Select or upload asset
    User->>Commerce: Request quote
    Commerce->>Workflow: Emit quote requested
    User->>Commerce: Create order
    Commerce->>Workflow: Emit order created
    Workflow->>Asset: Request BAT validation if required
    User->>Workflow: Validate BAT
    Workflow->>Production: Create production job
    Production->>Base44: Sync internal task
    Production->>Workflow: Emit production completed
